source.name: CCRB: Age of Substantiated Cases Measured from the Date of Report 2005 - 2009
source.description: A statistical breakdown of the age of Civilian Complaint Review Board (CCRB) substantiated cases, by year, measured from the date of the reports in the years 2205 through 2009.The age of the docket is measured by the number of open cases at the end of each reporting period.
